properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from  Suwannee River to Keaton Beach out 20 NM; Coastal waters from Okaloosa-Walton County Line to Mexico Beach out 20 NM; Coastal Waters From  Ochlockonee River to Apalachicola FL out to 20 Nm; Apalachee Bay or Coastal Waters From Keaton Beach to Ochlockonee River Fl out to 20 Nm; Coastal Waters from Mexico Beach to Apalachicola out 20 NM
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 22 at 4:10AM EST until January 22 at 10:00AM EST by NWS Tallahassee FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northeast winds 20 knots. Seas 2 to 4 feet are expected.

* WHERE...Nearshore Gulf waters from the Walton-Okaloosa County
line to the Ochlockonee River out 20 nautical miles, and
Nearshore Gulf waters from the Ochlockonee River to the
Suwannee River out 20 nautical miles.

* WHEN...Until 10 AM EST /9 AM CST/ this morning.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 10 AM EST /9 AM CST/ THIS MORNING
